**ConfigStore Trait**：
```rust
#[async_trait]
pub trait ConfigStore: Send + Sync {
    async fn load_token(&self) -> Result<Option<String>>;
    async fn save_token(&self, token: &str) -> Result<()>;
    async fn clear_token(&self) -> Result<()>;
    async fn get_or_create_device_id(&self) -> String;
}
```

